{"tid":999404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港高官拍片鼓勵長者搵工做","createTime":"2019-01-28T16:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T03:52:01.000Z","uid":28195,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"454e0f74a282f2e697f6a54271afdd4db2212206","tid":999404,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T16:13:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/長者高官拍片鼓勵長者/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%98%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%2F&d=MbUnvTePhOYiotiF0kn9oV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=06f07270\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%98%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%2F&h=ab725bfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/長者高官拍片鼓勵長者/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/0_Go4Mi_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F0_Go4Mi_1200x0.png&h=d9fd6f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n筆者又有新感想，醒起其實高官想鼓勵長者搵工的話，自己拍片鼓勵佢哋就得啦，因為本屆政府已經以身作則，聘請多名無能長者做官，證明長者搵工係冇．難．度。<br />\n例如，<strong>羅致光</strong>可以拍片說：「我 65 歲，高分低能，都有人請我做局長，you can do it!」<br />\n<strong>林鄭</strong>可以拍片：「我 61 歲，做官以嚟冇咩政策有過好下文，又唔識用八達通又唔識買廁紙，都有人搵我做特首，you can do it!」<br />\n<strong>張建宗</strong>：「我 68 歲，做咁耐官冇人講得出有過咩政績，一樣升到政務司，you can do it!」<br />\n<strong>陳茂波</strong>：「我 63 歲，又囤地又劏房，都做到發展局長同財政司，you can do it!」<br />\n<strong>鄭若驊</strong>：「我 60 歲，犯法僭建一樣做到律政司，you can do it!」<br />\n<strong>劉江華</strong>：「我 61 歲，只係個輸咗選舉的賣剩貨垃圾桶，都賺緊 30 幾皮，you can do it!」<br />\n<strong>楊偉雄</strong>：「我 63 歲，冇人知我講緊乜話，都搵到工，you can do it! 不過我見過 steve jobs 㗎&hellip;&hellip;」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong>陳帆</strong>：「我 60 歲，非常平凡，都撈到局長做，you can do it!」"},{"pid":"df66467cbbbcf9f1391c1d9f9733cd4434477a7d","tid":999404,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T00:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1d08fc9e59190ebd19da0eaa47b043e4ad1952","tid":999404,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e259ac51fc17a94c0cc5e25bc18c237e6fa8753a","tid":999404,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8076801716d660ac4eaad2963e9586207ce7d9d0","tid":999404,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:44:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88da747b8699b179f090aa3e55ca04e4eabb0e1d","tid":999404,"uid":76009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:51:36.000Z","msg":"整段 AI Fake 片就攪鬼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c3819010bbe640f3e6cafb791f370ec2738af8","tid":999404,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:54:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b90a8f03ab24078f28dcf3047f3525f4dca6e6c","tid":999404,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88da747b8699b179f090aa3e55ca04e4eabb0e1d","tid":999404,"uid":76009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:5